	<template name='Information.Font'>	
		<Name>Terminal</Name>
		<Size>8</Size>
		<Color>FFFFFFFF</Color>
	</template>	

	<window name='ComBot_SkillQueue'>
		<Visible>1</Visible>
		<BackGroundColor></BackGroundColor>
		<Border>0</Border>
		<X>200</X>
		<Y>300</Y>
		<Width>400</Width>
		<Height>400</Height>
		<TitleBar>
			<Width>100%</Width>
			<Height>20</Height>
			<Border>0</Border>
			<BackgroundColor>FF000000</BackgroundColor>
			<Children>
				<Text name='ComBot_SkillQueue_TitleBar_Title'>
					<X>0</X>
					<Y>3</Y>
					<Width>100%</Width>
					<Height>20</Height>
					<Alignment>Center</Alignment>
					<Text>SkillQueue Configuration</Text>
				</Text>
				<button	Name='Close'>
					<X>r40</X>
					<Y>0</Y>
					<Width>40</Width>
					<Height>20</Height>
					<Text>Close</Text>
					<OnLeftClick>
						ui -unload "&filepath;/SkillQueue"
					</OnLeftClick>
				</button>
			</Children>
		</TitleBar>
		<Children name="ComBot_SkillQueue_Children">
			<Frame name="ComBot_SkillQueue_Frame">
				<X>0</X>
				<Y>5</Y>
				<Width>100%</Width>
				<Height>100%</Height>
				<BackgroundColor>FF000000</BackgroundColor>
				<Border>1</Border>
				<BorderColor>FFFFFFFF</BorderColor>
				<Children name="ComBot_SkillQueue_Frame_Children">
					<Text name='obj_SkillQueueInformation'> 
						<Font template='Information.Font' />
						<X>1%</X> 
						<Y>1%</Y> 
						<Width>98%</Width> 
						<Height>18%</Height> 
						<Wrap />
						<VerticalAlignment>Center</VerticalAlignment>
						<Text>SkillQueue is a MiniMode to automatically fill your skill queue whenever it drops below 24 hours.  Skills which are already at level 5 which are added to this queue will be ignored when they are processed.  Skill which are not injected will stay queued and will be injected and queued up whenever a book is found in your ship's cargo hold or the personal hangar of a station.</Text>
					</Text>

					<listbox name='SkillQueue'>
						<X>1%</X> 
						<Y>19%</Y> 
						<Width>98%</Width> 
						<Height>60%</Height> 
						<OnLoad>
							Script[ComBot].VariableScope.SkillQueue:UpdateUI
							This.SortType:Set[user]
						</OnLoad>
						<OnSelect>
							UIElement[Skill@ComBot_SkillQueue_Frame@ComBot_SkillQueue]:SetText[${This.SelectedItem.Text}]
						</OnSelect>
					</listbox
					<textentry name='Skill'>
						<X>1%</X> 
						<Y>80%</Y> 
						<Width>98%</Width> 
						<Height>9%</Height> 
					</textentry>
					<button name='Add'>
						<X>1%</X> 
						<Y>90%</Y> 
						<Width>49%</Width> 
						<Height>9%</Height> 
						<OnLeftClick>
							Script[ComBot].VariableScope.SkillQueue:Add[${UIElement[Skill@ComBot_SkillQueue_Frame@ComBot_SkillQueue].Text}]
						</OnLeftClick>
					</button>
					<button name='Remove'>
						<X>50%</X> 
						<Y>90%</Y> 
						<Width>49%</Width> 
						<Height>9%</Height> 
					</button>
				</Children>
			</Frame>
		</Children>
	</window>
	
</ISUI>
